data.description: This impressive 5-bedroom, 3.5 bath residence holds a remarkable reputation as a highly sought-after Masters Tournament rental property in the esteemed River Oaks Subdivision. Embrace the elegance of a farmhouse-style dwelling while relishing the advantages of a central location. The home features a delightful rocking chair front porch, welcoming guests through double doors into a spacious two-story foyer. Carefully crafted hardwood floors enhance the kitchen, great room, and dining room, creating a seamless flow throughout the living spaces. The expansive open-concept gourmet kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances, custom cabinets, an eat-in area, and a generous island, effortlessly connecting to the great room that showcases a captivating brick fireplace. The main floor boasts a luxurious owner's suite, complete with a freestanding tub, tiled shower, dual vanities, and an expansive walk-in closet. Upstairs, you will find four sizable bedrooms complemented by two jack and jill bathrooms, as well as a bonus room, offering ample space for a growing family. Perfect for hosting gatherings, the outdoor area boasts a covered stamped patio and a custom-built bar. This remarkable home deserves your undivided attention as it promises an extraordinary living experience. This property has the capability to do a VA assumable loan at 3%!! Owner is offering $5000 towards closing cost. Easy to show!!
